de.larssh.utils.time

Class CloseableStopwatch

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.larssh.utils.time.Stopwatch
      • de.larssh.utils.time.CloseableStopwatch
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AutoCloseable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    LoggingStopwatch

    public abstract class CloseableStopwatch
extends Stopwatch
implements AutoCloseable
    Abstract and synchronized implementation of a closeable Stopwatch. Once a CloseableStopwatch is closed no more checkpoints can be created and sinceStart() and sinceLast() return durations based on the stopwatches stopping time.

    Extending class are meant to be used inside try-with-resource blocks.

    close() can be called multiple times while all but the first call are ignored.
